snippet.textDisplay:
Beautiful female singer has a great voice, but her portion of the rendition is weak poetry in comparison with "Afreen afreen"  lyrics, it is not more than nursery rhyme!! To give this portion space they have cut off the most robust and wild part of the lyrics 
"Aankhen Unchi Hui To Dua Ban Gayi ....
Aankhen Nichi Hui To Haya Ban Gayi...
Jhuk Kar Uthi To qaza Ban Gayi...
Aur Uth Kar Jhuki To Adaa Ban Gayi"
This rendition is more like well furnished version but Ustad Fateh Ali Khan has the aura of wilderness and folkloric tone. No offence no comparison both are beautiful just mentioning the difference. Respect from Bangladesh...
